  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1248",
  "title": "*List: allow to provide an itemComponent",
  "body": "There's currently no way to override the rendered item component in RefinementList, Menu, HierarchicalMenu and possibly others.\n\nAs soon as a user provides an itemComponent then the default itemComponent is no more used and the user will have to provide a react component being passed the data and the refine method to bind.\n",
